도 or 또한

'additive particle'

used with subject like 가 and 는 / subject particle
adds meaning similar to 'too' or 'also'


think of diff applications for 'too'
i like her > i like him, too
i like her > you like her too
^can refer to diff or same subject

^choosing 도 or 또한 is like this
도 for same subject
또한 for diff / in spoken lang, 도 flexible for both tho